data.current_description: Exports a copy of all or a subset of documents from Google Cloud Firestore to another storage system, such as Google Cloud Storage. The output of an export may only be used once the associated operation is done. If an export operation is cancelled before completion it may leave partial data behind in Google Cloud Storage.
